rComments: Ne fait que survoler la matière. Il lit ses powerpoints qui ne vont pas en profondeur. Les examens sont TRÈS faciles. Pour ce qui en est travaux, il n'est pas clair dans ce qu'il veut.

He is very knowledgable of the material, although I found that the seminars weren't very organized or very analytically stimulating.  It would have been nice to have more of a seminar style class, rather than a lecture style with him talking at us instead of with us, especially since the material could have been extremely interesting to discuss.
